# 📁 DocVault

> A modern full-stack document management application built with **FastAPI**, **React**, and **PostgreSQL**.

DocVault is a simple yet production-oriented document management system that allows users to upload, download, and manage files through a clean web interface. The project focuses on building a complete full-stack application with modern development practices while keeping the architecture easy to understand.

---

## ✨ Features

- 📤 Upload documents
- 🔍 Search documents
- ⬇️ Download documents
- 🗑️ Delete documents
- 🎨 Modern responsive UI
- 🔄 RESTful API
- 🗄️ PostgreSQL database
- ⚡ FastAPI backend
- ⚛️ React + Vite frontend

---

# 🏗️ Architecture

```
                React + Vite
                     │
              REST API (HTTP)
                     │
                FastAPI Backend
                     │
        SQLAlchemy + Alembic
                     │
               PostgreSQL Database
                     │
              Local File Storage
```

